name: Whiting Environmental
overview:
Welcome to Whiting Environmental Building Inspection. Founded in 1998, Whiting Environmental Building Inspection has developed a reputation as a leader in the fields of home inspection, indoor air quality and indoor environmental management. Our mission is to provide the highest level of service and value to our clients.

Whether you are buying, selling or already own your home, Whiting Environmental Building Inspection can provide the answers to your questions. Trained in building science and the latest technology our inspectors are able to provide a variety of services to allow you to make the best decisions for your home.
